---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services"
  page="services"
  description="Modular IT advisory services for growing businesses—reduce cost, risk, and complexity, starting with a Technology Health Check."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">Services</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT helps growing businesses reduce technology cost, risk, waste, and complexity across systems, tools, and vendors.
          Our support is practical, business-focused, and modular, so you can start where needed, continue where value is clear, and stop at any stage.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          For Brisbane-focused advisory context, see our <a href="/it-consulting-brisbane" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">IT consulting Brisbane</a> page, our broader <a href="/it-consulting" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">IT consulting advisory page</a>, or <a href="/it-services-brisbane" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Brisbane IT services</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
             style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/case-studies"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white">
            View case studies
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24 space-y-10">
      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Recommended first step</div>
        <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-2">Technology Health Check</h2>
        <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Quickly identify cost leaks, risk hotspots, tool overlap, and operational friction across your technology environment.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Best when you need clarity before committing budget, changing vendors, or launching new initiatives.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
          If you are exploring this step, see <a href="/insights/signs-your-business-has-outgrown-ad-hoc-it-decisions" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Signs your business has outgrown ad hoc IT decisions</a> for a practical leadership view.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/technology-health-check"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
             style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
            Start here
          </a>
          <a href="/contact"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white">
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Offer stack</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Engage in one area or combine offers into a modular advisory path that fits your business priorities.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6 border border-white/20">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl"><a href="/technology-health-check" class="hover:underline">Technology Health Check</a></h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Surfaces your highest-impact opportunities to reduce waste, tighten risk, and simplify decision-making.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when you need a practical baseline and clear next actions.</p>
            <a href="/technology-health-check" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Start here →</a>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">90-Day IT Priorities Plan</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Turns findings into a focused 90-day plan with quick wins, owners, and sequencing.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when your team needs momentum without overcommitting resources.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6 border border-white/20">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl"><a href="/it-support-and-fractional-cto/" class="hover:underline">Aurora ICT Total Care</a></h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Worry-free IT care across planning, leadership and service — not an MSP package, but tailored support, roadmap guidance, digital transformation support and Fractional CTO oversight.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when your business needs one tailored package rather than separate support and strategy providers.</p>
            <a href="/it-support-and-fractional-cto/" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Explore Total Care →</a>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Vendor and SaaS Review</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Reviews vendors, contracts, and tool overlap to improve value, reduce waste, and simplify your stack.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when costs are rising or platforms feel duplicated and hard to manage.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Cyber Risk Quick Wins Review</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Identifies practical control improvements that reduce risk quickly without heavy transformation work.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when leadership needs immediate, sensible risk reduction steps.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">AI Readiness Session</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Clarifies where AI can add measurable business value and what guardrails are required for safe adoption.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when evaluating AI opportunities but unsure where to start.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Strategic Roadmap Support</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Builds 1-year, 3-year, and 5-year technology direction aligned to business growth and operating realities.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Relevant when you need long-term clarity across priorities, budget, and delivery sequencing.</p>
            <a href="/it-strategy-roadmap" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Learn more →</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">How Aurora ICT works</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT operates as a modular advisory journey: start with the most relevant service, continue only where value is clear, and pause at any stage as your internal capability strengthens.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">1. Assess</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Map current costs, risks, systems, vendors, and immediate friction points.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">2. Prioritise</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Translate findings into practical priorities, quick wins, and staged decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">3. Support</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Add targeted advisory support only where it lifts outcomes across delivery, vendors, and risk.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">4. Simplify</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Leave your business with clearer ownership, lower complexity, and stronger self-sufficiency.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Broader advisory and delivery support</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Start with a focused offer like the Technology Health Check, then add broader strategic, technical, or delivery support only where it helps your business move faster with less risk. Security-focused teams can also review our <a href="/cybersecurity-smb-brisbane" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">cybersecurity advisory page</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Virtual CTO / Fractional Technology Leadership</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Senior leadership support for prioritisation, governance, vendor direction, and clearer executive technology decisions.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Cloud &amp; Systems Architecture</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Design and refine scalable, resilient platforms that reduce complexity while supporting growth and performance needs.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Cyber Risk Reduction</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Apply practical control improvements that lower business risk and strengthen security posture without unnecessary overhead.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Project &amp; Program Oversight</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Improve delivery confidence through stronger planning, accountability, vendor coordination, and milestone visibility.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">AI &amp; Automation</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Identify practical automation and AI opportunities that improve efficiency while maintaining sensible governance and control.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>



      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Not sure where to start?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Book a free initial consultation and we will help you choose the right first step based on your current business priorities.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          You can also browse practical guidance in our <a href="/insights" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Insights library</a>, including roadmap and security-focused articles.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact"
           class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
           style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
          Book your free initial consultation
        </a>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
